      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. MONTGAUDRY lost out by 1.5L delivering a third place finish over 1600m at Saint-Cloud. Looks capable of returning to winning ways. 5. MARLOWE followed up a 0.5L triumph in a 1500m handicap at Cagnes-sur-Mer with a 3L sixth contesting a 1400m event at Saint-Cloud. Expected to challenge. 14. HAYEJOHN produced good form on the AW in recent months including when securing a 0.75L victory over 1400m at Chantilly AW. Strong claims of defying a 3.5kg rise in weights. Revisiting turf 15. ASTON CLINTON is another to consider after managing a 3L fifth competing in a 1600m handicap at Chantilly AW.\",\"runners\":[7,5,14,15],\"exclusive\":false}",
